item.title: CVE-2021-3832|2024-09-17T02:36:13.483Z -- %C3%A1rtica -- integria%20ims
item.description: Integria IMS in its 5.0.92 version is vulnerable to a Remote Code Execution attack through file uploading. An unauthenticated attacker could abuse the AsyncUpload() function in order to exploit the vulnerability.
